data.description: One story home with basement in China Grove sitting on 1.4 acres with no HOA! LVP floors in the kitchen, dining area and living room. Original hardwood floors in one of the bedrooms.There is enough LVP flooring to cover the primary bedroom and additional bedrooms that has already been purchased that will convey. Play set and trampoline convey with this gorgeous property. Endless opportunities for the 1500 sqft basement. Pool table may convey for $1500 with a separate bill of sale.
